snippet: Box, a business data storage and management company, is expanding as part of plans for an expected initial public offering in 2014.
abstract: Box, London-based online data storage and management company will open new offices in Germany and France as part of lead-up to initial public offering in 2014.
lead_paragraph: Box, a business data storage and management company, is expanding as part of plans for an expected initial public offering in 2014.
